{"name":"Fanged Deserter","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"class","data":{"abilities":"<p>Built like a Bull, roll 3d6+2 for Strength. Not a Bright Spark, roll 3d6-1 for Agility and Presence. Normal Agility tests are DR14 instead of DR12, excluding defense. Illiterate; you are incapable of understanding scrolls. If you begin with one then reroll, eat it or use it as toilet paper. You also begin with one of the following:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Crumpled Monster Mask</li>\n<li>The Brown Scimitar of Galgenbeck</li>\n<li>Wizard Teeth</li>\n<li>Old Sig&ucirc;rd&rsquo;s sling</li>\n<li>Ancient Gore-Hound</li>\n<li>The Shoe of Death's Horse</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>EARLIEST MEMORIES, D6</p>\n<ol>\n<li>A burnt-black building in Sarkash. Your home?</li>\n<li>A derelict rotting ship rolling endlessly across a grey sea.</li>\n<li>A brothel in Schleswig. Quite a friendly environment.</li>\n<li>Sleeping with dogs in the corner of an inn, waiting for someone to return.</li>\n<li>Following an army in eastern W&auml;stland.</li>\n<li>Suckling a wolf in the wild of Bergen Chrypt.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","armorTableDie":"1d4","description":"You have thirty or so friends who never let you down: YOUR TEETH. Disloyal, deranged or simply uncontrollable, any group that didn’t boot you out you left anyway. But your parliament of teeth—enormous, protruding, thick and sharp—have always been your allies. Bite attack: DR10 to attack, d6 damage. You must be close to your target. 1–2 on d6 chance the enemy gets a free attack.","omenDie":"1d2","startingAgility":"3d6-1","startingHitPoints":"1d10","startingItems":"morkborg.class-fanged-deserter,Clumsy\nmorkborg.class-fanged-deserter,Illiterate\nmorkborg.class-fanged-deserter,Bite Attack","startingPresence":"3d6-1","startingRolls":"morkborg.rolls-fanged-deserter,Fanged Deserter Items,1\nmorkborg.rolls-fanged-deserter,Earliest Memories,1","startingSilver":"2d6*10","startingStrength":"3d6+2","startingToughness":"3d6","weaponTableDie":"1d10"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/fanged_deserter.png","effects":[],"_id":"2hjl45o4vXOgRgfq"}
